lead_paragraph: Blue Jackets goalie Sergei Bobrovsky might be getting a little weary after starting all but two of Columbus' first 21 games. His teammates made sure he didn't have to do a lot of heavy lifting Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Anderson, Bobrovsky Lead Blue Jackets Past Lightning 5-1
